从史兰德改为萨兰德
from Sjlander to Salander.

686
01:20:06,173 --> 01:20:08,041
萨拉...萨兰德 两者音似
Zala... Salander.

687
01:20:12,045 --> 01:20:14,848
萨拉千古很少回家
Zalachenko was seldom home.

688
01:20:15,449 --> 01:20:19,620
但偶尔出现在伦德格坦的公寓
But showed up inbetween at the apartment in Lundagatan.

689
01:20:21,622 --> 01:20:25,626
他喝醉了 虐待她妈妈
He got drunk, abused the mother.

690
01:20:26,326 --> 01:20:30,631
强奸她 然后就不见踪影
Forced her to sex. Then he disappeared.

691
01:20:31,465 --> 01:20:35,035
这样的事发生过很多次
This happened dozens of times.

692
01:20:35,702 --> 01:20:40,007
民政局本该阻止此事 可他们毫无作为
The municipality should have intervened, but they did nothing.

693
01:20:41,909 --> 01:20:45,612
直到1993年
Not until 1993.

694
01:20:48,615 --> 01:20:50,617
发生了什么事
What happened then?

695
01:20:55,389 --> 01:20:58,092
谋杀未遂 企图用燃烧弹杀死生父
Attempted murder. Wanted to kill father with fire bomb.

696
01:20:58,659 --> 01:21:01,628
丽莎白斯那时候12岁
Lisbeth was 12 years old.

697
01:21:03,163 --> 01:21:04,389
当丽莎白斯发现
Zalachenko laughed

698
01:21:04,390 --> 01:21:06,667
母亲在厨房地板上不省人事时
when Lisbeth found her mother

699
01:21:07,367 --> 01:21:09,803
萨拉千古得意不已
unconscious on the kitchen floor.

700
01:21:11,071 --> 01:21:15,175
他出门上车 但丽莎白斯追上他
He went out and got in his car, but Lisbeth ran after him

701
01:21:15,943 --> 01:21:21,348
把装满汽油的牛奶盒扔进汽车
and threw a milk carton with gasoline into the car.

702
01:21:29,823 --> 01:21:32,292
男人被活生生烧成了火把
A man burns like a torch.

703
01:21:36,430 --> 01:21:38,265
老天
My god.

704
01:21:38,699 --> 01:21:43,003
这次 事情有了结果
And this time it had consequences.

705
01:21:43,837 --> 01:21:45,806
丽莎白斯被带走
Lisbeth was taken

706
01:21:46,306 --> 01:21:50,010
最终被送进阿普萨拉的儿童精神科病房
and ended up on a children's psychiatric ward in Uppsala.

707
01:21:51,845 --> 01:21:53,767
在她离开的这段时间
Her mother was admitted to hospital

708
01:21:53,768 --> 01:21:55,516
她妈妈被一家医院收留
during those few years she had left.

709
01:21:58,152 --> 01:22:00,421
她再没有康复
She never recovered.

710
01:22:02,990 --> 01:22:07,361
有关她的精神问题... 彼得·泰勒柏林
About her having psychiatric problems... Peter Teleborian.

711
01:22:08,195 --> 01:22:11,598
他让她接受精神科护理
He got her admitted to psychiatric care.

712
01:22:15,669 --> 01:22:20,384
而另一方面 她的父亲 亚历山大·萨拉千古
On the other hand, her father, Alexander Zalachenko,

713
01:22:20,385 --> 01:22:20,908
未受任何惩罚
received no punishment.

714
01:22:23,610 --> 01:22:25,212
该死
God damn ...

715
01:22:41,662 --> 01:22:42,930
你好
Hello.

716
01:22:43,831 --> 01:22:45,360
亚历山大·萨拉千古
Alexander Zalachenko.

717
01:22:45,361 --> 01:22:47,167
这个名字有没有让你想到什么
Does the name tell you anything?

718
01:22:47,835 --> 01:22:50,490
没 记者招待会要开始了
No. The press conference is about to start.

719
01:22:50,490 --> 01:22:52,639
他是丽莎白斯·萨兰德的父亲
He's Lisbeth Salander's father.

720
01:22:55,342 --> 01:22:58,011
她在1993年用燃烧弹袭击了他
She assaulted him with a fire bomb in 1993,

721
01:22:58,579 --> 01:23:00,762
警察也调查过此事
And the police investigated the matter.

722
01:23:00,762 --> 01:23:03,117
注意是秘密警察
Make a note it was the security police.

723
01:23:03,951 --> 01:23:07,254
为什么 萨拉千古为他们工作
Why? Zalachenko worked for them.

724
01:23:07,921 --> 01:23:10,991
他不可能被指认 官方来讲他是不存在的
He could not be identified. Officially he doesn't exist.

725
01:23:11,658 --> 01:23:14,072
他没有任何公共记录
He's not listed in any public records.

726
01:23:14,073 --> 01:23:15,129
那你怎么知道的
And how do you know this?

727
01:23:15,829 --> 01:23:19,633
如果旧档案还在 你可以去找找看
You will go find the old case file, if it's in there some place.

728
01:23:24,071 --> 01:23:27,374
我觉得它会帮我们找到萨拉千古
I think it can lead us to Zalachenko.

729
01:23:28,675 --> 01:23:32,513
我坚信他和安斯基得的谋杀案有关
I'm convinced he's got something to do with the murders in Enskede.

730
01:23:33,247 --> 01:23:36,550
很可能还参与了彼尤曼律师的谋杀
Mostly likely the murder of solicitor Bjurman as well.

731
01:23:37,151 --> 01:23:39,887
不是丽莎白斯·萨兰德
Contrary to Lisbeth Salander?

732
01:23:40,487 --> 01:23:44,792
凶器上有她的指纹 我知道这听起来很荒诞
Her fingerprints are on the weapon. I know it sounds peculiar.

733
01:23:45,592 --> 01:23:46,553
的确是荒诞
Peculiar, indeed.

734
01:23:46,554 --> 01:23:49,163
可你为什么对丽莎白斯·萨兰德这么感兴趣
Why are you so interested in Lisbeth Salander?

735
01:23:49,930 --> 01:23:52,166
如果她是无辜的 那为什么不自己出面
If she's innocent, why won't she turn herself in?

736
01:23:52,699 --> 01:23:54,501
丽莎白斯是个
Lisbeth is

737
01:23:58,072 --> 01:24:01,241
...很注重隐私的人
... a very private person.

738
01:24:01,909 --> 01:24:06,447
我不喜欢你总是试图捏造线索
I don't like that you're constantly trying to create a lead.

739
01:24:07,247 --> 01:24:08,433
我们的问题已经够多了
We have enough problems.

740
01:24:08,433 --> 01:24:11,218
我们不用私家侦探就能解决这个案子
We'll solve this case without private investigators.

741
01:24:26,300 --> 01:24:28,068
欢迎回来
Welcome back.

742
01:24:32,339 --> 01:24:37,211
波罗·罗伯托火海勇救米里亚姆
Paolo Roberto saved Miriam from the flames.

743
01:24:44,318 --> 01:24:47,621
你还认为丽莎白斯对周围的人存在威胁吗
Do you still consider Lisbeth a danger to her surroundings?

744
01:24:48,288 --> 01:24:51,458
她枪击了一个人 她有武器
She has shot a person. She is armed.

745
01:24:52,092 --> 01:24:54,795
我们一定会抓住她
Of course we'll capture her.

746
01:24:55,362 --> 01:24:58,165
你知道米里亚姆被绑架的幕后指使者是谁吗
Do you know who was behind Miriam's kidnapping?

747
01:24:58,766 --> 01:25:02,202
我们将这个问题交给首席调查人员巴兰斯基
We'll pass on that question to lead investigator Bublanski.

748
01:25:02,903 --> 01:25:06,407
此次清晨枪击事件包括一名男性
A man involved in this morning's shooting incident

749
01:25:07,174 --> 01:25:11,779
可能是早先绑架案中的司机
was possibly the driver during a previous kidnapping attempt.

750
01:25:12,679 --> 01:25:16,250
是遭受枪击的人吗 无可奉告
The man who was shot? No comment.

751
01:25:18,118 --> 01:25:21,955
殴打米里亚姆·吴和波罗·罗伯托的人
The one abusing Miriam Wu and Paolo Roberto

752
01:25:22,723 --> 01:25:24,758
没有留下任何线索
left no traces.

753
01:25:25,259 --> 01:25:27,828
你们有没有关于他的描述
And you have no description of him?

754
01:25:28,362 --> 01:25:31,632
我们绘制了这张肖像
We've had this drawing made.

755
01:25:32,299 --> 01:25:35,736
是根据目击者的描述绘制的
It's based on witness descriptions.

756
01:25:36,470 --> 01:25:41,408
是一名高大 健壮 35至40岁的男性
It's a large, muscular male around 3540 years old.

757
01:25:42,342 --> 01:25:46,180
像是一名健美运动员 金色短发
Built like a body builder. Short, blonde hair.

758
01:25:46,947 --> 01:25:49,231
记者招待会后
The drawing will be made available

759
01:25:49,231 --> 01:25:51,985
每一位都可以拿到这张画像
to everybody after the press conference.

760
01:25:54,822 --> 01:26:00,194
警方称他们尚未逮捕那位28岁女性
Police informed that they have not apprehended the 28 year old woman

761
01:26:01,161 --> 01:26:04,431
她在斯兰格地区小屋枪击事件之后
which after the shooting incident in the cabin area at Stragne

762
01:26:05,099 --> 01:26:08,635
骑着摩托车逃离现场
fled the scene on a motorcycle.

763
01:26:09,369 --> 01:26:13,040
据已有消息 本案可能与黑帮有关
According to information available it may be gang related.

764
01:26:14,708 --> 01:26:17,077
他们他妈的什么线索都没有
They have no fucking clue!

765
01:26:19,213 --> 01:26:22,850
巴兰斯基不听 他们一条道跑到黑
Bublanski didn't listen. They are locked in on one single lead.

766
01:26:23,550 --> 01:26:25,863
如果警察逮捕了丽莎白斯
If the police apprehends Lisbeth,

767
01:26:25,864 --> 01:26:27,287
什么事都可能发生
anything can happen.

768
01:26:27,988 --> 01:26:30,090
你去哪 回家
Where are you going? home.

769
01:26:30,324 --> 01:26:31,147
要我陪你吗
Should I come with?

770
01:26:31,148 --> 01:26:33,694
不 这种情况下我可不是个好伴
No, I wouldn't be pleasant company at the moment.

771
01:26:34,361 --> 01:26:37,131
你不必如此
You don't have to be.

772
01:26:49,176 --> 01:26:51,712
泰勒柏林 你的话更为关键
And you, Teleborian, are even more critical.

773
01:26:52,279 --> 01:26:56,683
你说她没有接受治疗只是谣言
You're calling it a scandal that she did not receive treatment.

774
01:26:57,484 --> 01:27:00,954
我不会对个案进行评价
I won't comment on individual cases.

775
01:27:01,655 --> 01:27:06,593
但是我必须说 某些复杂病例
But I have to say that certain complex cases

776
01:27:07,461 --> 01:27:09,930
需要合格的治疗
requires qualified treatment.

777
01:27:10,464 --> 01:27:13,967
我只能说 我对三个人失去生命感到遗憾
I can only say I'm sorry that three people lost their lives

778
01:27:14,635 --> 01:27:18,806
这是精神科治疗预算消减的后果
as a result of the budgetary cuts in psychiatric care.

779
01:27:19,640 --> 01:27:22,042
这么说这名女性应该被关起来
So this woman should be locked up?

780
01:27:25,412 --> 01:27:28,382
有一些病人需要被管制
There are patients who should be institutionalized

781
01:27:29,016 --> 01:27:32,486
而不是在社会上自由来去
instead of moving around freely in society.

782
01:28:04,985 --> 01:28:07,254
我知道萨拉千古是谁
I know who Zalachenko is.

783
01:28:07,721 --> 01:28:10,824
我和帕姆格兰谈过 知道了泰勒柏林的事
I have talked to Palmgren and understand Teleborian's part,

784
01:28:11,558 --> 01:28:14,962
还有你被关在儿童精神科医院的原因
and why you had to be locked up in the children's psychiatric ward.

785
01:28:15,696 --> 01:28:17,931
我觉得我知道是谁杀了道格和米娅
I believe I know who killed Dag and Mia.

786
01:28:18,499 --> 01:28:21,104
可我不理解彼尤曼的部分
But I don't understand Bjurman's part in this.

787
01:28:21,104 --> 01:28:23,303
现身吧 我们能解决一切
Turn yourself in, we can solve this.

788
01:29:00,040 --> 01:29:02,409
很感激有你这位朋友
Thank you for being my friend.

789
01:29:27,000 --> 01:29:28,702
是我
It's me.

790
01:29:29,703 --> 01:29:31,004
好
Okay.

791
01:29:43,250 --> 01:29:45,452
他是长这样吗
Did he look like this?

792
01:29:47,121 --> 01:29:51,225
他很可怕 是个真正的魔鬼
He was horrible. A real monster.

793
01:30:00,033 --> 01:30:02,870
妈的 妈的 对不起
Fuck. Fuck, I'm sorry.

794
01:30:05,472 --> 01:30:08,308
他们在找你 但你知道吗
You're the one they were looking for. But you know that?

795
01:30:11,612 --> 01:30:13,280
你做什么了
What have you done?

796
01:30:16,517 --> 01:30:20,087
波罗说布罗姆科斯特联系他想找到你
Paolo said Blomkvist contacted him to get to you.

797
01:30:22,623 --> 01:30:25,192
你们之间发生了什么 我要走了
What is there between you two? I have to go.

798
01:30:25,826 --> 01:30:29,463
你去哪 我有些事要完成
Where are you going? There is something I have to finish.

799
01:30:30,164 --> 01:30:31,632
他妈的是什么...
What the fuck...?

800
01:30:42,443 --> 01:30:45,112
刚刚这里来了位女士
There was a lady in here.

801
01:30:45,713 --> 01:30:49,016
金色短发 她刚走
A short blonde, she left.

802
01:30:49,717 --> 01:30:52,720
我给你拿点帮助睡眠的东西 马上回来
I'll bring you something to help you sleep. I'll be right back.

803
01:31:27,554 --> 01:31:30,424
我早就该这么做了
I should've done it a long time ago.

804
01:31:57,818 --> 01:31:59,720
进去 进去
Inside. Inside!

805
01:32:01,655 --> 01:32:03,924
我要看你的租车记录
I want to see your records of rented cars.

806
01:32:04,491 --> 01:32:07,294
在电脑里 打开它
They are on the computer. Turn it on.

807
01:32:12,266 --> 01:32:14,401
过来 慢点
Come. Slowly.

808
01:32:21,709 --> 01:32:23,377
打开壁橱
Open the closet.

809
01:32:25,379 --> 01:32:27,247
把你的手机给我
Give me your cellphone.

810
01:32:29,049 --> 01:32:32,386
到壁橱里去 我没必要伤害你
Go inside the closet. And I won't have to hurt you.

811
01:32:40,327 --> 01:32:42,746
你的租赁合同在哪
Where do you keep your rental contracts?

812
01:32:42,747 --> 01:32:44,965
在架子上的一个文件夹里
In a folder on the shelf.

813
01:32:57,177 --> 01:33:00,748
我要租辆车 我放这儿1万块
I need to rent a car. I'm leaving 10 000 here.

814
01:33:01,415 --> 01:33:03,016
我会把车还你的
You will get your car back.

815
01:33:32,713 --> 01:33:35,716
很感激有你这个朋友
Thank you for being my friend.

816
01:33:49,663 --> 01:33:53,000
喂 我是米里亚姆 米里亚姆·吴
Hello, it's Miriam, Miriam Wu.

817
01:33:54,334 --> 01:33:57,171
你能顺道到医院来吗
Can you stop by the hospital?

818
01:33:59,640 --> 01:34:03,410
这么说她来过了 什么时候 几个小时前
So she's been here? When? A few hours ago.

819
01:34:04,111 --> 01:34:06,547
她有说要去哪吗
Did she say where she was going?

820
01:34:09,750 --> 01:34:11,919
没有 那不是丽莎白斯的风格
No, Lisbeth doesn't do that.

821
01:34:12,386 --> 01:34:16,090
如果她查到那个魔鬼 会被他杀害的
If she tracks down that monster, he'll kill her.

822
01:34:20,627 --> 01:34:22,796
给你 她忘了这些
Here. She forgot these.

823
01:34:23,330 --> 01:34:25,799
忘了 不是 是她掉的
Forgot? No, she dropped them.

824
01:34:26,366 --> 01:34:28,836
从她的背包里掉出来的
They fell out of her backpack.

825
01:34:30,337 --> 01:34:32,906
我不知道她住哪 你呢
I have no idea where she lives. Do you?

826
01:34:37,845 --> 01:34:41,915
这是什么 看上去像信箱钥匙
What is it? Looks like a Po box key.

827
01:35:01,969 --> 01:35:04,671
这个可以吗 好的谢谢
Can you use this? Yes please.

828
01:36:35,162 --> 01:36:36,663
喂
Hello?

829
01:37:20,974 --> 01:37:22,509
丽莎白斯吗
Lisbeth?

830
01:38:01,248 --> 01:38:02,946
高泽伯格交通台
Gotherburg Traffic Radio.

831
01:38:02,947 --> 01:38:06,155
在格罗伯文F90路上发生了交通事故
There's been an accident on Grabovern, road F90.

832
01:38:07,154 --> 01:38:11,258
事故导致交通拥堵 车流缓慢
The accident has caused traffic jams, and traffic is moving slowly.

833
01:38:17,531 --> 01:38:19,929
比斯克普斯的社会局呼吁
The social board in Biskopsgarden requests

834
01:38:19,929 --> 01:38:22,669
支持反对家庭暴力的措施
support for measures against domestic violence.

835
01:38:26,006 --> 01:38:28,409
它更应该被称作苹果核
It's most certainly called an apple core.

836
01:38:28,942 --> 01:38:31,378
回到序言
Back to pretentions.

837
01:38:31,879 --> 01:38:36,884
回想一下 你最得意的作品是哪一部
In retrospect, what is the most pretentious work you have written?

838
01:39:35,709 --> 01:39:37,981
这张照片是17岁的
This picture is 17 years old.

839
01:39:37,982 --> 01:39:40,080
他的名字是罗兰德·尼德曼
His name is Ronald Niederman.

840
01:39:40,948 --> 01:39:44,418
他被捕时18岁 今年35岁了
He was 18 when he was caught so today he's 35.

841
01:39:45,119 --> 01:39:48,155
你怎么弄到这照片的 汉姆伯格的健身房
Where did you get the picture? Dynamic in Hamburg.

842
01:39:48,756 --> 01:39:52,693
就像我跟米克说的 他不是拳击手
Like I told Micke, he's not worth jack shit as a boxer.

843
01:39:53,460 --> 01:39:56,021
但像拳击手一样移动步伐
But he moved like a boxer,

844
01:39:56,022 --> 01:39:57,598
所以一定有人教过
so somebody must've coached him.

845
01:39:58,332 --> 01:40:01,635
我已经给欧洲几个拳击健身房发了邮件
I Emailed several boxing gyms in Europe.

846
01:40:02,302 --> 01:40:06,006
告诉他们这边的情况 并对他进行了描述
Told them what had happened and tried to describe him.

847
01:40:07,508 --> 01:40:11,178
他身患一种疾病 天生无痛觉
He has an illness. He was born with analgesia.

848
01:40:12,913 --> 01:40:16,050
怎么回事 我查过了 是基因缺陷
What is that? I looked it up. Genetic error.

849
01:40:16,717 --> 01:40:19,987
神经突触没用 感觉不到疼痛
The nerve synapses do not work. You feel no pain.

850
01:40:57,758 --> 01:40:59,827
喂 喂 我是马琳
